  "prompt": "What will be my rank I scored 325 in neet?",
  "response": "Predicting your exact rank based on a NEET score of 325 can be challenging, as ranks depend on several factors, including the overall performance of candidates in that specific year, the number of test-takers, and the difficulty level of the exam. \n\nThat said, historical data suggests that a score of 325 may place you around a lower to mid-range rank, but it is important to check the official NEET results for more precise and up-to-date information regarding ranks and cut-offs for various colleges.\n\nFor the most accurate estimate, consider looking at the official NEET analysis for the year you took the exam or reach out to coaching institutes that provide rank predictions based on previous years' data.",
